The Bureau Australian Hourly Solar Irradiance Gridded Data includes DNI and GHI data from satellite observations.
<p>
Hourly Solar Irradiance Gridded Data is not based on a real-time product. Data is processed by the Bureau of Meteorology nominally at 3 monthly intervals.
